{
  "chapter": 13,
  "chapter_summary": "楚留香折断一点红宝剑，书信也在内力激荡下化为碎片。黑衣少年去而复返，惊慌躲入窗帘后。白玉魔率丐帮弟子驱蛇而来，欲追究灵蛇之死。楚留香如数家珍揭露白玉魔被逐出丐帮的丑史与奸杀罪行。白玉魔驱动毒蛇攻击，楚留香举手间尽毙二十余条毒蛇，笑言要炖三蛇羹。白玉魔正欲以毒掌出手，丐帮新任帮主南宫灵及时赶到，喝退白玉魔。南宫灵与楚留香、一点红寒暄周旋，欲追查黑衣少年下落。话锋突转，袖中双剑掷向窗帘——却只刺中一双空靴。楚留香大笑调侃，黑衣少年早已遁走无踪。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_yi_dian_hong",
      "speaker_name": "一点红",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好，果然是好武功，好身法!",
      "tone": "颤声",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 12,
      "line_end": 12
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "红兄承让了。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 14,
      "line_end": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yi_dian_hong",
      "speaker_name": "一点红",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这……这……",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 20,
      "line_end": 20
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "看来我命中注定，是瞧不着这封信的了。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 22,
      "line_end": 24
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yi_dian_hong",
      "speaker_name": "一点红",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "此……此信可是十分重要?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 26,
      "line_end": 26
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那也没什么。我拍断你的宝剑，本应向你道歉才是。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 30,
      "line_end": 32
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yi_dian_hong",
      "speaker_name": "一点红",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "终我一生，若再寻你动手，有如此剑。",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 34,
      "line_end": 36
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hei_yi_shao_nian",
      "text": "阁下来得正好，在下有事请教。",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 40,
      "line_end": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yi_dian_hong",
      "speaker_name": "一点红",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这些蛇邪门得很，是哪里来的?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 68,
      "line_end": 68
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_yi_dian_hong",
      "text": "红兄只怕是已惹上麻烦了。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 70,
      "line_end": 70
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "麻烦果然已来了。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 88,
      "line_end": 88
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yu_mo",
      "speaker_name": "白玉魔",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "侬竟敢害死本帮格灵蛇，阿是要死快哉?",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 90,
      "line_end": 90
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_bai_yu_mo",
      "text": "本帮?阁下说的`本帮`，却不知是哪一帮?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 94,
      "line_end": 94
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yu_mo",
      "speaker_name": "白玉魔",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "侬，你眼瞎了么?难道连丐帮门下都瞧不出来?",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 96,
      "line_end": 96
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_bai_yu_mo",
      "text": "丐帮子弟，我自然是瞧得出来的，只是阁下十余年前已被逐出丐帮，今日怎敢还自称丐帮弟子?",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 98,
      "line_end": 98
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yu_mo",
      "speaker_name": "白玉魔",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "不想你这黄口小儿，倒也知道我老爷子的来历。",
      "tone": "狂笑",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 100,
      "line_end": 102
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_bai_yu_mo",
      "text": "我若不知道你来历，谁知道你来历?你本姓白，只因作恶多端，又生得一身细皮白肉，所以江湖中人却将你唤作'白玉魔丐'，你反而自鸣得意，索性将'丐'字去掉，把自己名字叫做白玉魔。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 104,
      "line_end": 106
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yu_mo",
      "speaker_name": "白玉魔",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "说得好，还有呢?",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 110,
      "line_end": 110
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_bai_yu_mo",
      "text": "十余年前，你兽性大发，在苏州虎丘，一口气奸杀了十七位黄花处子，任老帮主一怒之下，已决心要将你以家法处死，谁知你倒也知机，竟早已躲起来了，任老帮主寻你不着，只有将你先逐出门墙。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 112,
      "line_end": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yu_mo",
      "speaker_name": "白玉魔",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "对，说得对极了。只是如今任老头子已死，新帮主不像他那么顽固无知，知道本帮若想重振声威，还得要老子这一双妙手来帮忙的，老子虽不屑吃这回头草，但瞧他一番好意，也就勉强回来了。",
      "tone": "狞笑",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 116,
      "line_end": 118
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "南宫灵虽然素来宽大为怀，这事做的却未免有欠考虑。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 122,
      "line_end": 124
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qi_dai_di_zi",
      "speaker_name": "七袋弟子",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "本帮帮主之决策，天下有谁敢任意批评?",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 126,
      "line_end": 126
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_qi_dai_di_zi",
      "text": "别人不敢，也许我倒是敢的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 128,
      "line_end": 128
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qi_dai_di_zi",
      "speaker_name": "七袋弟子",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "你算是什么东西?",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 130,
      "line_end": 130
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_qi_dai_di_zi",
      "text": "为什么到处都有人问我是什么东西?我明明不是东西，是人，和各位生得也没有什么不同，也许瞧起来还比各位顺眼些，各位难道这一点都分不清么?",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 132,
      "line_end": 132
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yu_mo",
      "speaker_name": "白玉魔",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "那么，我倒要请教你是何许人也，竟敢在我面前如此说话，莫非是活得不耐烦了么?",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 134,
      "line_end": 134
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_bai_yu_mo",
      "text": "谁说我活得不耐烦，我活得正觉有趣极了，世上的好酒是够喝一辈子，何况还有南宫灵那样的朋友时常来为我倒酒。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 140,
      "line_end": 142
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qi_dai_di_zi",
      "speaker_name": "七袋弟子",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "你认得我家南宫帮主?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 144,
      "line_end": 144
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_qi_dai_di_zi",
      "text": "我虽然想说不认得他，怎奈我这一辈子却从来不会说谎。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 146,
      "line_end": 148
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ba_dai_di_zi",
      "speaker_name": "八袋弟子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这莫非是他缓兵之计，好叫那小子逃走。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 150,
      "line_end": 152
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yu_mo",
      "speaker_name": "白玉魔",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那小子逃得了么，我老爷子早已在这里埋下了杀人的埋伏，连你也算上，这屋子里一个也休想活着出去。",
      "tone": "狞笑",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 154,
      "line_end": 156
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_bai_yu_mo",
      "text": "南宫灵若听见你对我这样说话，只怕要生气的。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 158,
      "line_end": 158
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yu_mo",
      "speaker_name": "白玉魔",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "既是如此，我就索性叫他生生气吧!",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 160,
      "line_end": 160
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我虽然不喜欢杀人，但对于杀蛇倒是从不反对的。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 164,
      "line_end": 166
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "秋风起矣，进补及时，只可惜我那甜儿不在这里，否则正好请她为我炖一盅又鲜又浓的三蛇羹。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 178,
      "line_end": 180
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_bai_yu_mo",
      "text": "咦!奇怪，你肚子里怎地有人在摇骰子，但瞧你的满脸霉气，摇出来的点子一定是个'一二三'。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 190,
      "line_end": 192
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yi_dian_hong",
      "speaker_name": "一点红",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "掌上有毒，要小心了。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 198,
      "line_end": 198
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_yi_dian_hong",
      "text": "你放心，毒不死我的。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 200,
      "line_end": 200
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yu_mo",
      "speaker_name": "白玉魔",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "谁说毒不死你?",
      "tone": "狞笑",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 202,
      "line_end": 202
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_nan_gong_ling",
      "speaker_name": "南宫灵",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "住手!",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 206,
      "line_end": 206
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_nan_gong_ling",
      "text": "南宫兄来得倒巧，方才小弟若是做了毒蛇们及时进补的活人羹，南宫兄日后岂非要少了个酒伴?",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 216,
      "line_end": 216
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_nan_gong_ling",
      "speaker_name": "南宫灵",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "幸好小弟还是早来了一步，否则本帮这三个有眼无珠的弟子，只怕已要变成楚兄的'三人羹'了。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 218,
      "line_end": 220
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_nan_gong_ling",
      "text": "你做了帮主，说话怎地也不肯规矩些?",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 222,
      "line_end": 222
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_nan_gong_ling",
      "speaker_name": "南宫灵",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "和楚兄这样的人说话，若是言语无趣，楚兄日后还肯交小弟这朋友么?但无论如何，本帮弟子无礼之罪，还是请两位恕过。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 224,
      "line_end": 226
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_nan_gong_ling",
      "speaker_name": "南宫灵",
      "listener": "char_qi_dai_di_zi",
      "text": "你们年纪也已不小了，怎地做事如此糊涂，也不问对方是谁，便胡乱出手，难道忘了本帮帮规了么?",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 228,
      "line_end": 228
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yu_mo",
      "speaker_name": "白玉魔",
      "listener": "char_nan_gong_ling",
      "text": "帮主也不必指着和尚骂秃驴，他两人并未出手，是我出手的。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 232,
      "line_end": 234
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_nan_gong_ling",
      "speaker_name": "南宫灵",
      "listener": "char_bai_yu_mo",
      "text": "既是如此，本座便要请问白师叔，为何不问清楚，便要胡乱出手伤人，莫非白师叔你又想退出本帮不成?",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 236,
      "line_end": 236
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yu_mo",
      "speaker_name": "白玉魔",
      "listener": "char_nan_gong_ling",
      "text": "咱们本是追那恶徒而来，瞧见这……这两位在此，自然要认为是这两位将那小子藏起来的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 238,
      "line_end": 240
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_nan_gong_ling",
      "speaker_name": "南宫灵",
      "listener": "char_bai_yu_mo",
      "text": "你可曾问过他两位了么?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 242,
      "line_end": 242
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yu_mo",
      "speaker_name": "白玉魔",
      "listener": "char_nan_gong_ling",
      "text": "没……没有。",
      "tone": "慌张",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 244,
      "line_end": 244
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_nan_gong_ling",
      "speaker_name": "南宫灵",
      "listener": "char_bai_yu_mo",
      "text": "既未问过，你又怎知是他两位将那人藏起来的?那人凶险恶毒，人所难容，他两位又怎会庇护于他?",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 246,
      "line_end": 246
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_nan_gong_ling",
      "speaker_name": "南宫灵",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "何况有'中原一点红'与'盗帅'楚留香在此，天下无论什么人到了这里，也都该恭恭敬敬，客客气气，你们又凭什么如此无礼?",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 250,
      "line_end": 250
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yu_mo",
      "speaker_name": "白玉魔",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "原来阁下便是楚香帅，我白玉魔今日栽在盗帅手下，倒也不丢人，这里事有帮主来了，也用不着我再管……咱们后会有期吧!",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 266,
      "line_end": 266
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_nan_gong_ling",
      "speaker_name": "南宫灵",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "此人近年行径虽已改，但气量仍是难免褊狭，出手仍是难免鲁莽，但望楚兄莫要见怪才好。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 270,
      "line_end": 272
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_nan_gong_ling",
      "text": "别人不怪我，我已心满意足了，我又怎会怪别人。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 274,
      "line_end": 274
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_nan_gong_ling",
      "speaker_name": "南宫灵",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "不想楚兄与红兄的侠驾全都来到此间，此地小弟虽未久居，却也时常来往，勉强也算得半个主人，少时定要与两位快饮几杯。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 276,
      "line_end": 278
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_nan_gong_ling",
      "text": "你们终年要饭，难道也问别人要酒么，好好，我不管你们的酒是要来的，还是抢来的，有人请客喝酒，我从不肯错过……红兄你也莫要错过了，需知那不花钱的酒，喝来滋味是分外不同的。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 280,
      "line_end": 282
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yi_dian_hong",
      "speaker_name": "一点红",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我从不喝酒。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 284,
      "line_end": 284
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_yi_dian_hong",
      "text": "如此大好适口充肠之物，若是不喝，岂非对不住自己?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 286,
      "line_end": 286
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yi_dian_hong",
      "speaker_name": "一点红",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "酒能使人手颤心软，杀人就不怕了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 288,
      "line_end": 288
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_yi_dian_hong",
      "text": "若为杀人而不喝酒，简直好像为了怕拉屎而不吃饭一样，不但荒谬已极，而且惨无人道，红兄你……",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 290,
      "line_end": 290
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gai_bang_di_zi",
      "speaker_name": "丐帮弟子",
      "listener": "char_nan_gong_ling",
      "text": "后面的屋子，弟子们已随诸长老与葛长老全都查过了，冷某人也已送交公孙护法，并无那恶徒的踪影。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 292,
      "line_end": 294
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_nan_gong_ling",
      "speaker_name": "南宫灵",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "既是如此，便请楚兄将那人交出来吧!",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 296,
      "line_end": 296
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_nan_gong_ling",
      "text": "你说的是什么人?",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 298,
      "line_end": 298
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_nan_gong_ling",
      "speaker_name": "南宫灵",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "不瞒楚兄，小弟也弄不清那人的来历，只知他身法轻便，武功甚高，两天前曾在赵官镇伤了本帮十余弟子，还偷去了本帮一些重要之物，方才又伤了本帮宋护法，是以本帮对他是万万不能放过的。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 300,
      "line_end": 302
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_nan_gong_ling",
      "text": "哦……有这样的人?这样的事?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 304,
      "line_end": 304
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_nan_gong_ling",
      "speaker_name": "南宫灵",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "楚兄真的不知此人?",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 306,
      "line_end": 306
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_nan_gong_ling",
      "text": "我纵然要打别人的主意，也不会打到你们丐帮头上的。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 308,
      "line_end": 308
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_nan_gong_ling",
      "speaker_name": "南宫灵",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "如此最好……",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 312,
      "line_end": 312
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_nan_gong_ling",
      "speaker_name": "南宫灵",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "到了此刻，阁下还不肯出来么?",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 322,
      "line_end": 324
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_nan_gong_ling",
      "speaker_name": "南宫灵",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 326,
      "line_end": 326
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好好的窗帘，被砍成两截，一双上等的小牛皮靴子，也被刺了两个洞，南宫兄不觉太可惜了么?",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 340,
      "line_end": 340
    }
  ],
